<template>
  <v-app>
    <v-navigation-drawer app v-model="drawer">

      <template v-slot:prepend>
        <v-list-item
            two-line
            prepend-avatar="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/women/81.jpg"
            title="Admin"
            subtitle="已登入"
            style="padding-bottom: 16px;"
        ></v-list-item>
      </template>

      <v-divider></v-divider>

      <v-list v-model:opened="User" nav density="compact">
        <v-list-group>
          <template v-slot:activator="{ props }">
            <v-list-item v-bind="props" title="用户" value="User" prepend-icon="mdi-account-circle"></v-list-item>
          </template>

          <v-list-item
              v-for="([title, icon], i) in users"
              :key="i"
              :value="title"
              :title="title"
              :prepend-icon="icon"
          ></v-list-item>
        </v-list-group>
      </v-list>



    </v-navigation-drawer>

    <v-app-bar app color="#1F7087">

      <template v-slot:prepend>
        <v-app-bar-nav-icon variant="text" @click.stop="drawer = !drawer"></v-app-bar-nav-icon>
      </template>

      <v-app-bar-title>管理后台</v-app-bar-title>

    </v-app-bar>

    <!-- Sizes your content based upon application components -->
    <v-main style="height: 100vh;">

      <!-- Provides the application the proper gutter -->
      <v-container fluid>

        <!-- If using vue-router -->
        <router-view></router-view>
      </v-container>
    </v-main>

    <v-footer app>
      <!-- -->
    </v-footer>
  </v-app>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  name: "adminMain"
}
</script>

<style scoped>

</style>
